ss=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">FINE MOTOR TOYS: Not only a great creative outlet for art, but the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse art kit also allows little ones to develop their fine motor skills through drawing, painting, and coloring! Mixing paint, trying to color between the lines, and perfecting their artwork helps with the development of their dexterity, hand-eye coordination, and imagination</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 11.7” x 1.5” x 12.5”inches; Weight: .86lbs; Color: Blue; Ages: 3+</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>Disney Mickey Mouse Kids 40pc Art Supplies Coloring Marker Crayon Paint Pad Set</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">34.99</span></h2>\n                <p>This immersive creative Disney Mickey House and Friends art kit features all their favorite characters from the Disney Junior series! The portable art kit contains 40 items to keep your little Mickey Mouse and budding artist busy! The art kit includes an exciting coloring book, six colorful markers, twelve vibrant watercolors with a paintbrush and mixing tray, six colorful markers, ten crayons, six high-quality colored pencils, a pencil sharpener, and an eraser that all securely fit in the art supplies tote provided. With multiple mediums to choose from, your child will never get bored while on the go with this super fun art kit!\n\nBe ready for any Mickey Mouse artistic adventure! This ideal Disney Mickey Mouse and Friends Art supplies kit can be used at preschool, elementary school, day camps, or for any imaginative adventures with Mickey and his friends at the Mickey Mouse Clubhouse. Your child will easily keep their art supplies secure with this carrying case craft supplies tote with a handle.\n \nWith a multitude of different exciting art mediums found in this colorful craft supplies tote, your little one can unleash their creativity and be able to showcase their own Disney artwork. An ideal birthday present or holiday gift, this Mickey Mouse and Friends art activity set will provide hours of entertainment by creating artwork from Mickey Mouse and all his friends!</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2026</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n        </div>\n",
